&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;The Rotherham NHS Foundation Trust&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Appointment of Consultant Breast Surgeon &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Candidates with specialist registration (or those within six months of CCT) are invited to apply for the post of full time Consultant Oncoplastic Breast Surgeon. It is anticipated that successful candidate has broad experience and expertise in management of breast diseases and be able to fully support the Rotherham Breast Oncoplastic Service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful candidate will be the third consultant in the team, who are supported by an associate specialist equivalent and a specialist registrar. The surgical team is fully supported by breast care nurses, radiology, pathology and oncology.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For more information and job details please refer to the NHS Jobs Website and search using reference number:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Closing date for receipt of application is 19th November 2020.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
